---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Trucker Copilot | Built for the Business of Trucking"
  description="Trucker Copilot connects drivers, carriers, transportation data, and specialty finance infrastructure so completed work can move toward payment with less friction."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:2.5rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">About</span>
      <h1>Built for the people who move the freight.</h1>
      <img class="photo mt-2" src="/img/photos/driver-dock.jpg" alt="Driver leaning against his truck at a distribution center at sunset, checking his phone" loading="eager" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top:1rem;">
    <div class="container container--narrow prose">
      <p>
        Trucker Copilot was created around a simple reality: the financial process should not begin
        after the load is complete. The information required to understand and fund the transaction
        already exists while the freight is moving. The problem is that it has traditionally been
        scattered across drivers, dispatchers, paper, email, transportation systems, and finance
        companies.
      </p>
      <p>
        Trucker Copilot brings that activity together. Drivers capture what happened. Carriers see
        what is moving. Finance providers receive better evidence. FactorEvo powers the financial
        infrastructure behind the transaction.
      </p>
      <p>
        The result is one connected ecosystem built around transportation, from the cab to the
        funding decision.
      </p>

      <h2>Our purpose</h2>
      <p>Give every legitimate carrier a clearer path from completed work to trusted financial access.</p>

      <h2>Our operating belief</h2>
      <blockquote>
        <p style="margin:0;"><strong>The strongest financial decision begins with better evidence. Better evidence begins closer to the work.</strong></p>
      </blockquote>

      <h2>Company</h2>
      <p>
        Trucker Copilot is part of the FactorEvo Group Holdings ecosystem. The mobile platform is
        being developed in strategic partnership with CargoNerd to serve drivers, owner operators,
        dispatchers, and carrier fleets across the transportation industry.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    headline="Join the network built around trucking."
    primaryLabel="Join the Network"
    primaryHref="/download"
    secondaryLabel="Contact Us"
    secondaryHref="mailto:info@truckercopilot.com"
  />
</Base>
